Kindness N.V., a Bahamas-based firmowned by U.K. investor and Bahamas resident John Templeton,said it has acquired 137,900 shares of Hausereman Inc, or 5.9pct of the total outstanding common stock.    In a filing with the Securities and Exchange Commission,Templeton said he bought the shares for investment purposesonly and has no intention of seeking control of the company. Reuter&#3;